title: Tickled
description:
Tig and Cheryl finally take on "Tickled," a much-requested doc with more twists than a tickle-fight. The True Story duo discuss their tickling history, research the origins of slipping on a banana peel, and compare Cheryl's pronunciation of "documentary" to that of a native New Zealander. *this episode spills beans* (tigandcheryltruestory@gmail.com)
